TAMPA PACKING COMPANY, INC., et al., v. J. J. CLAMAR 20 So. (2nd) 396

June Term, 1944

January 5, 1945 Division B Rehearing denied January 29, 1945 John S. Edwards, for appellants. J. C. Rogers, for appellee. PER CURIAM:

Affirmed on authority of Jacksonville T. & K. W. Ry. Co. v. Lockwood, 33 Fla. 573, 15 So. 327, and Supreme Lodge K. of P. v. Lipscomb, 50 Fla. 406, 39 So. 637.

BUFORD, C. J., BROWN, THOMAS and SEBRING, JJ., concur.
